Indoda eneminyaka elinganiselwa ku-30 ishayiswe yimoto ntambama ngoMgqibelo lapho kuhlangana khona umgwaqo * -Innes noMngeni. Imigwaqo iseduze nenkundla iMabhida obekukhandelene kuyo izinkumbi zabantu ebezizothamela inkulumo kaMengameli Cyril Ramaphosa. Kuthiwa indoda ibigqoke umfaniswano we-ANC ngesikhathi kwenzeka ingozi. Yenzeke ngesikhathi izama ukuwela umgwaqo. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, uthe amaphoyisa avule idokodo lokubulala kungahlosiwe. “NgoMgqibelo ntambama indosa ishayiswe yimoto yashonela khona lapho. Imbangela yengozi iyaphenywa. Amaphoyisa aseDurban Central aphenya icala lokubulala ngokungenhloso,” kusho uCapt Gwala. Umufi ubengakakhonjwa ngamalungu omndeni wakhe.